------------------------------------------------------
	biber
------------------------------------------------------

biber is used in 'tool' mode to cleanup raw bib file generated from mendeley

	biber --tool --output_encoding=ascii thesis.bib

command used in cleanup_bib.bat, the local biber.conf configuration file is used, the file 'thesis_bibertool.bib' is generated with clean bib content to be used by the thesis


NOTE: 
sometime, even after biber proecssing, there may still be some strange characters left in 'thesis_bibertool.bib'. If so, manual correction is needed.

Always backup a working version of 'thesis_bibertool.bib'!


References:
- http://tex.stackexchange.com/questions/1453/command-line-tools-for-some-bibtex-database-manipulations
- http://sourceforge.net/projects/biblatex-biber/files/biblatex-biber/1.8/documentation/





